raw_text: The balcony is off of the living room Bathroom 1 is off of the master bedroom and other 2 bedroom Bathroom 2 is off of the east side of the living room next to the kitchen oppostite of balacony Common room 1 is off of the hallway thorouh the living room Common room 2 is off of the hallway through the living room The kitchen is off of the east side of the living room opposite of the balacony also near bathroom.
